data.news_body: The Board of Directors of the Company at their meeting held today, took on record the Un-audited Financial Results ('UFR') for the quarter and half year ended September 30, 2022. The Limited Review Report ('LRR') thereon received from the Statutory Auditors of the Company was placed at the said Board Meeting.  The UFR along with LRR are being uploaded on your website along with this letter.
